amds revision history
---------------------

Version 1.04 - Dec 7, 2000?
--------------------------

- Now passes reaction variables to AMDSGRAPHCMD in stdin.

- Bugfixes
  - Crashes with "Invalid font in XChangeGC (0xffffffff) fixed
  - Debug printouts from reading default vars from the db removed

- Internal
  - Development moved from euler.itereu.de to my Linux Pc
  - makefile: workaround added to avoid "double CbFree" errors

Version 1.03 - Mar 30, 1999
---------------------------

- New
  - Default values from the database added for variables.

- Bugfixes
  - "Show graph" could work incorrectly in the main view.
  
- Internal
  - GetVarEx() added
  - Reaction::Vars added for database defaults.

Version 1.02 - Mar 30, 1999
---------------------------

- New
  - Variable definitions in existing files updated using the configuration.
  - Changes to the database no longer cause crashes when loading existing
    *.amd files.
  - Several bugs fixed.

Version 1.01 - Apr 30, 1997
---------------------------

- New
  - "Show text" now works in TeX files.


Version 1.0 - Nov 4, 1996
-------------------------

First program version.
